458
00:34:41.840 --> 00:34:44.110
Obat salep emas ini kusiapkan khusus
untuk Nyonya Besar.

459
00:34:44.360 --> 00:34:46.150
Kalau kau berani menyentuhnya lagi...

460
00:34:46.150 --> 00:34:47.070
Ning Yuxuan!

461
00:35:02.840 --> 00:35:03.590
Hati-hati.

462
00:35:03.920 --> 00:35:05.000
Kenapa kau datang?

463
00:35:07.110 --> 00:35:08.960
Kenapa aku datang?

464
00:35:11.880 --> 00:35:13.110
Muxu, bantu aku bangun.

465
00:35:15.750 --> 00:35:16.630
Ayo, Nyonya Besar.

466
00:35:23.700 --> 00:35:24.700
