566
00:39:44.630 --> 00:39:46.590
Lalu, mereka sekeluarga sudah
pindah ke Barat Laut.

567
00:39:47.630 --> 00:39:49.320
Barat Laut?

568
00:39:50.000 --> 00:39:52.480
Apalagi, setelah kau menikahi Adipati,

569
00:39:52.670 --> 00:39:55.710
