apa pun lagi dengannya!

595
00:40:58.320 --> 00:40:59.630
Nyonya Besar, pelankan suaranya.

596
00:41:00.880 --> 00:41:01.710
Muxu,

597
00:41:02.840 --> 00:41:06.270
